                {"question": "Can custom pages handle paid registration?", "answer": "Yes. Stripe Checkout handles payment processing at 2.9% + $0.30 per transaction. The attendee clicks Register, completes payment on Stripe's hosted checkout page, and redirects to your confirmation page. No PCI compliance burden on your site."},
